text: The Morocco women's national handball team is the national team of Morocco. It is governed by the Royal Moroccan Handball Federation and takes part in international handball competitions. ==African Championship record== *1987 – 8th *2002 – 9th *2012 – 10th *2018 – 10th ==External links== *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Handball National team
